OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FA coroner has ruled the death of a
OL,7,Ffour-year-old boy, from sepsis, was
OL,8,F"avoidable", our reporter Olivia
OL,9,FGuthrie has the details
OL,11,FA four-year-old boy who had been taken
OL,12,Fto hospital four times in a week was
OL,13,F"probably" septic while he was seen by
OL,14,Fmedical staff in the hours before he
OL,15,Fdied, an inquest heard.
