OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FDaniel Klosi died from sepsis at the
OL,7,FRoyal Free Hospital in Camden, north
OL,8,FLondon, on April 2 last year, having
OL,9,Fbeen taken to the hospital four times
OL,10,Fin a week, including twice in one day,
OL,11,Fby his anxious parents.
OL,13,FAs a trainee GP with little experience
OL,14,Fin paediatrics, Dr Gautham Benoy said
OL,15,Fhe could see that Daniel was an
OL,16,F"unwell child" when he saw him on the
OL,17,Fevening of April 1.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@NO]
