OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FDr Benoy, who was working at the
OL,7,Fhospital and was called as the number
OL,8,Fof acutely unwell patients in A&E was
OL,9,Fbacking up, said he could see Daniel
OL,10,Fwas an unwell child, with sunken eyes,
OL,11,Fcracked lips, and that he looked
OL,12,Flikely to be severely dehydrated.
OL,14,FDr Benoy also said he had abdominal
OL,15,Fpain and appeared "quite restless and
OL,16,Fappeared in distress when I tried to
OL,17,Fexamine him".
OL,26,@wD@SOUyD@LO]
