OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FHe also believed he was possibly "at
OL,7,Frisk of sepsis" and some of the
OL,8,Ffeatures to look out for included
OL,9,Flethargy, rash, fever, blood pressure
OL,10,Fand heart rate.
OL,12,FThe coroner told Dr Benoy that Daniel
OL,13,Fhad no rash or elevated heart rate,
OL,14,Fwhich he saw as a "reassuring
OL,15,Ffeatures", but he would not know what
OL,16,Flethargy for this child looked like.
