OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FDr Benoy turned to Daniel's parents as
OL,7,Fhe answered a question on whether it
OL,8,Fwould have been appropriate for him to
OL,9,Fhave spoken to them to try to allay
OL,10,Ftheir concerns.
OL,12,FHe told them: "I understand. I am
OL,13,Fsorry for everything you have been
OL,14,Fthrough."
OL,16,FDr Amisha Singh, who works in
OL,17,Fconsultant paediatrics, had been on a
OL,18,Fbusy shift seeing patients in A&E and
OL,19,Fpaediatrics.
