OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FOn March 26 he and Daniel's mother,
OL,7,FLindita Alushi, noticed Daniel was
OL,8,F"wheezing and had a barking cough",
OL,9,Fand took him to the Royal Free
OL,10,Femergency department, where he was
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with crepitation of the
OL,12,Flungs.
OL,14,FThey returned on March 30 when a
OL,15,Fdoctor and nurse said Daniel had
OL,16,Fpicked up a virus, and that he should
OL,17,F"go home and rest", the father's
OL,18,Finquest statement said.
