OL,3,CBoy, 4, was probably septic when seen
OL,4,Cby medical staff, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe parents called 111 and were booked
OL,7,Fin for triage at the hospital on April
OL,8,F1 after Daniel "suddenly stopped
OL,9,Feating and drinking", and he was seen
OL,10,Fat about 1pm.
OL,12,FMr Klosi said he was "told his chest
OL,13,Fwas clear and he was suffering from a
OL,14,Fvirus" but "felt as if the doctor was
OL,15,Ffixated on telling me Daniel had a
OL,16,Fvirus rather than finding out what the
OL,17,Freal problem was".
